snippet.title: Turnabouts Of The Father [BLIND] Part 1: The Leviathan
snippet.description:
[A Visual Novelty]

I couldn't stay away. As foreshadowed on Twitter, I'm back with some hot fancase action, an alternate universe Apollo with severe father issues, roped into a rather unique premise of a trial!

Case by DudeWithAMask! Play it here: http://www.aaonline.fr/player.php?trial_id=69624
